Interface Cache.Entry<T extends Cache.Entry<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the hash table entry that implements this interface.
    All Superinterfaces:

    public static interface Cache.Entry<T extends Cache.Entry<T>>
extends Comparable<T>
    An interface for hash table entries that extends the Comparable interface and defines methods required for the management of entries in the hash table.

    Viktor
